@TomSweeneyRedHat  Basically yes. In pseudo code:
```
attempt to pull image from the registry
if pull succeeded:
  run pulled image
else:
  print "warning failed to pull image, trying local storage"
  look in local storage
  if found in local storage:
    run found image
  else:
    raise error "image not found from registry or local storage"
```
